All right, I yield.

215
00:13:44,230 --> 00:13:45,430
看啊
Behold!

216
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:47,480
托尔
Thor...

217
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:50,040
-奥丁森  -不
- Odinson. - No.

218
