我们更喜欢被称为"魔法师"
The preferred term is "Master of the Mystic Arts."

252
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:20,740
别管了
You can leave that now.

253
00:16:21,470 --> 00:16:24,670
好吧  男巫  你是谁  我为什么要在乎
All right, wizard. Who are you? Why should I care?

254
00:16:24,930 --> 00:16:26,680
