What do you drink?

260
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:42,320
不喝茶
Not tea.

261
00:16:45,910 --> 00:16:47,500
我有一份关注名单
So, I keep a watch list

262
00:16:47,500 --> 00:16:49,130
都是来自其他世界
of individuals and beings from

263
