other realms that may be a threat to this world.

264
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:55,210
你的领养弟弟  洛基  就是其中之一
Your adopted brother, Loki, is one of those beings.

265
00:16:55,490 --> 00:16:56,900
的确该加上他
He's a worthy inclusion.

266
