我们在找我父亲
We're looking for my father.

268
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:06,720
那么  如果我告诉你奥丁在哪
So, if I were to tell you where Odin was,

269
00:17:06,990 --> 00:17:09,380
所有相关人士都会马上回阿斯加德吗
all parties concerned would promptly return to Asgard?

270
00:17:09,380 --> 00:17:10,390
是的  马上
Promptly.

271
00:17:10,410 --> 00:17:12,290
太好了  我来帮你吧
Great! Then I'll help you.

272
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:14,810
如果你知道他在哪  为什么不联系我
If you knew where he was, why didn't you call me?

273
