Anyway, my father is no longer in exile.

281
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:37,720
麻烦你告诉我他在哪  我就能带他回家了
So if you could tell me where he is, I can take him home.

282
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,860
没问题  他在挪威
Gladly. He's in Norway.

283
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:41,860
我就是查看一下
I'm just seeing

284
00:17:41,860 --> 00:17:46,290
这则咒语是否要为阿斯加德人做些调整
whether this incantation requires any Asgardian modifications.

285
00:17:46,910 --> 00:17:47,590
不用
Nope.

286
00:17:48,740 --> 00:17:49,910
我们不需要那个
We don't need that.

287
00:17:55,660 --> 00:17:57,760
你能不能别那么做了
Will you stop doing that?

288
00:17:58,490 --> 00:18:02,110
我可以...我需要你一根头发
Can I... I need just one strand of your hair.

289
