Let me explain something. My hair is not to be meddled with.

290
00:18:13,730 --> 00:18:14,900
我们完全可以用走的
We could have just walked.

291
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,980
他在等你了
He's waiting for you.

292
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:20,480
好
All right.

293
00:18:21,190 --> 00:18:22,650
别忘了你的伞
Don't forget your umbrella.

294
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:23,430
是啊
Yes.

295
00:18:31,810 --> 00:18:32,700
