Sorry.

296
00:18:35,220 --> 00:18:36,390
来了
There we go.

297
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:39,650
我还得要回我弟弟
I suppose I'll need my brother back.

298
00:18:40,540 --> 00:18:41,490
对了  好的
Yeah. Right.

299
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:50,830
我都下落30分钟了
I have been falling for 30 minutes!

300
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:52,970
他就交给你了
You can handle him from here.

301
00:18:53,210 --> 00:18:56,070
