Handle me? Who are you?

304
00:19:00,120 --> 00:19:00,740
洛基
Loki.

305
00:19:00,740 --> 00:19:02,330
你是什么术士吗
You think you're some kind of sorcerer?

306
00:19:02,330 --> 00:19:03,850
你个二流货  别以为你...
Don't think for one minute, you second-rate...

