I know. We've come to take you home.

314
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:53,930
回家  是啊
Home, yes.

315
00:19:55,780 --> 00:19:58,170
你们母亲  她在召唤我
Your mother, she calls me.

316
00:20:00,610 --> 00:20:01,550
