I know we failed you.

322
00:20:22,840 --> 00:20:24,410
但我们可以弥补的
But we can make this right.

323
00:20:25,210 --> 00:20:26,200
是我辜负了你们
I failed you.

324
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:30,210
诸神黄昏已经到来
It is upon us. Ragnarok.

325
