我们小时候  有一次
There was one time when we were children,

1303
01:26:58,460 --> 01:27:00,030
他变成了一条蛇
he transformed himself into a snake,

1304
01:27:00,030 --> 01:27:01,380
他知道我喜欢蛇
and he knows that I love snakes.

1305
01:27:01,380 --> 01:27:03,270
我捡起蛇  好好欣赏
So, I went to pick up the snake to admire it,

1306
01:27:03,270 --> 01:27:04,880
结果他变了回去
and he transformed back into himself

1307
01:27:04,880 --> 01:27:06,080
大喊  "嘿  是我"
and he was like, "Yeah, it's me!"

1308
01:27:06,080 --> 01:27:09,260
然后捅了我  我们当时才八岁
And he stabbed me. We were eight at the time.

1309
01:27:09,690 --> 01:27:10,810
我们要偷飞船的话
If we're boosting a ship

1310
01:27:10,810 --> 01:27:12,810
得把王宫的守卫引开
we're gonna need to draw some guards away from the palace.

1311
01:27:12,820 --> 01:27:14,770
放出野兽吧
Why not set the beast loose?

1312
01:27:14,790 --> 01:27:15,510
闭嘴
Shut up.

1313
01:27:15,530 --> 01:27:16,740
你们有野兽
You guys have a beast?

1314
01:27:16,740 --> 01:27:19,210
没有  没什么野兽  他在胡说
No, there's no beast. He's just being stupid.

1315
01:27:19,300 --> 01:27:20,930
我们要挑起革命
We're going to start a revolution.

1316
01:27:21,030 --> 01:27:22,820
-革命  -我过会儿再解释
- Revolution? - I'll explain later.

1317
01:27:22,820 --> 01:27:25,220
-他是谁来着 -过会儿再解释
- Who's this guy again? - I'll explain later.

1318
01:27:26,260 --> 01:27:28,780
你拉出来的
Is that some sort of protoplasm,

1319
01:27:28,780 --> 01:27:31,390
是原生质吗  还是卵
all the stuff that's coming out of you, or are they eggs?

1320
01:27:32,490 --> 01:27:33,620
看起来像卵
Looks like eggs.

1321
01:27:43,240 --> 01:27:44,640
我找寇格
I'm looking for Korg.

1322
01:27:44,640 --> 01:27:45,620
谁找我
Who's asking?

1323
01:27:46,190 --> 01:27:47,110
我知道是你
I know you're asking.

1324
01:27:47,120 --> 01:27:49,840
还有别人吗  还是只有你
Is there anyone else asking, or is it just you?

1325
01:27:49,910 --> 01:27:52,060
雷王向你问好
The Lord of Thunder sends his best.

1326
01:27:55,460 --> 01:27:57,270
革命开始了
The revolution has begun.

1327
01:27:57,730 --> 01:27:59,790
革命  怎么会这样
Revolution? How did this happen?

1328
01:27:59,890 --> 01:28:00,650
不知道
Don't know.

1329
01:28:01,510 --> 01:28:03,980
但角斗场的服从圆盘主机
But the arena's mainframe for the Obedience Disks

1330
01:28:03,980 --> 01:28:05,220
被关掉了
have been deactivated

1331
01:28:05,220 --> 01:28:07,340
奴隶都武装起来了
and the slaves have armed themselves.

1332
01:28:07,340 --> 01:28:08,850
我不喜欢那个词
I don't like that word.

1333
01:28:08,990 --> 01:28:10,330
哪个  主机吗
Which? Mainframe?

1334
01:28:10,490 --> 01:28:12,840
不是  我怎么会不喜欢"主机"
No. Why would I not like "mainframe"?

1335
01:28:12,840 --> 01:28:15,120
S开头的那个
No, the "S" word.

1336
01:28:15,120 --> 01:28:18,260
抱歉  在职囚犯们都武装起来了
Sorry, the prisoners with jobs have armed themselves.

1337
01:28:19,210 --> 01:28:20,920
这样好多了
Okay, that's better. That's better.

1338
01:28:26,860 --> 01:28:28,770
听着  我们应该谈谈
So, listen. We should talk.

1339
01:28:30,140 --> 01:28:31,180
我不同意
I disagree.

1340
01:28:31,590 --> 01:28:34,380
我们家从来就不擅长开诚布公
Open communication was never our family's forte.

1341
01:28:34,380 --> 01:28:35,870
可不是呢
You have no idea.

1342
01:28:36,010 --> 01:28:38,580
我们上次谈过后发现的真相很是了不得
Been quite the revelation since we last spoke.

1343
01:28:39,170 --> 01:28:39,850
你们好
Hello.

1344
01:28:48,830 --> 01:28:50,320
奥丁让我们聚在一起
Odin brought us together.

1345
01:28:51,190 --> 01:28:53,840
他的死让我们分裂  还挺诗意
It's almost poetic that his death should split us apart.

1346
01:29:00,290 --> 01:29:01,800
我们现在与陌生人无异
We might as well be strangers now.

1347
01:29:02,440 --> 01:29:05,520
两位王子  各自漂泊
Two sons of the crown, set adrift.

1348
01:29:08,740 --> 01:29:10,160
你不是不想谈吗
Thought you didn't wanna talk about it.

1349
01:29:11,980 --> 01:29:12,860
问题是...
Here's the thing.

1350
01:29:13,120 --> 01:29:14,740
我可能留在萨卡更好
I'm probably better off staying here on Sakaar.

1351
01:29:14,740 --> 01:29:16,380
我也这么想
That's exactly what I was thinking.

1352
01:29:18,590 --> 01:29:19,880
你刚刚是在同意我说的话吗
Did you just agree with me?

1353
01:29:19,900 --> 01:29:21,650
这地方太适合你了
Come on, this place is perfect for you.

1354
01:29:21,750 --> 01:29:23,550
野蛮  混乱  无法无天
It's savage, chaotic, lawless...

1355
01:29:23,550 --> 01:29:24,910
弟弟  你会在这儿如鱼得水的
Brother, you're gonna do great here.

1356
01:29:25,480 --> 01:29:27,490
你就真这么瞧不起我
Do you truly think so little of me?

1357
01:29:29,390 --> 01:29:31,210
洛基  我曾非常看重你
Loki, I thought the world of you.

1358
01:29:32,230 --> 01:29:34,210
我以为我们能永远并肩战斗
I thought we were gonna fight side by side forever.

1359
01:29:34,210 --> 01:29:37,770
但最终  你是你  我是我
But at the end of the day, you're you and I'm me.

1360
01:29:38,540 --> 01:29:40,680
我也说不好  或许你还有一丝良心  但
I don't know, maybe there's still good in you, but...

1361
01:29:41,120 --> 01:29:44,310
说实话  我们早已分道扬镳
let's be honest, our paths diverged a long time ago.

1362
01:29:49,250 --> 01:29:49,940
是啊
Yeah.

1363
01:29:51,510 --> 01:29:53,800
或许我们还是再也不要见面了比较好
It's probably for the best that we never see each other again.

1364
01:29:53,830 --> 01:29:55,260
这不是你一直想要的吗
It's what you always wanted.

1365
01:29:59,460 --> 01:30:00,720
我们来演"喊救命"吧
Hey, let's do "Get Help."

1366
01:30:01,400 --> 01:30:02,820
-什么  -"喊救命"
- What? - "Get Help."

1367
01:30:03,000 --> 01:30:03,500
不
No.

1368
01:30:03,500 --> 01:30:04,570
-来嘛  你最喜欢了  -我非常讨厌
- Come on, you love it. - I hate it.

1369
01:30:04,570 --> 01:30:06,440
-这招多棒啊  每次都好使  -太丢人了
- It's great. It works every time. - It's humiliating.

1370
01:30:06,440 --> 01:30:07,680
-你有更好的计划吗  -没有
- Do you have a better plan? - No.

1371
01:30:07,680 --> 01:30:08,560
那就这么办
We're doing it.

1372
01:30:09,010 --> 01:30:11,040
我才不要演"喊救命"
We are not doing "Get Help."

1373
01:30:12,020 --> 01:30:13,580
救命  求你们了
Get help! Please!

1374
01:30:13,580 --> 01:30:14,770
我弟弟快死了
My brother, he's dying.

1375
01:30:14,780 --> 01:30:16,640
救命  帮帮他吧
Get help! Help him!

1376
01:30:18,860 --> 01:30:19,760
经典
Classic.

1377
01:30:20,240 --> 01:30:21,200
我还是讨厌
Still hate it.

1378
01:30:21,410 --> 01:30:23,380
-太丢人了  -我又不丢人
- It's humiliating. - Not for me, it's not.

1379
01:30:24,010 --> 01:30:25,990
好了  她让我们上哪艘船来着
Now, which one's the ship she told us to get?

1380
01:30:26,540 --> 01:30:27,420
司令号
The Commodore.

1381
01:30:28,060 --> 01:30:28,760
好的
Right.

1382
01:30:31,670 --> 01:30:33,850
不过我觉得应该也没什么用
Though I feel it won't make much of a difference.

1383
01:30:37,300 --> 01:30:38,270
洛基
Loki.

1384
01:30:39,430 --> 01:30:41,040
我知道我背叛过你很多次
I know I've betrayed you many times before,

1385
01:30:41,040 --> 01:30:42,890
但这次真不是针对你
but this time it's truly nothing personal.

1386
01:30:42,890 --> 01:30:46,040
抓到你的赏金会让我过得很阔绰
The reward for your capture will set me up nicely.

1387
01:30:46,040 --> 01:30:47,630
你果然从不是个重感情的人
Never one for sentiment, were you?

1388
01:30:47,630 --> 01:30:49,260
无情会过得更轻松些
Easier to let it burn.

1389
01:30:49,720 --> 01:30:50,690
我同意
I agree.

1390
01:30:59,210 --> 01:31:00,550
看起来好痛
That looks painful.

1391
01:31:01,600 --> 01:31:04,450
亲爱的弟弟  你越来越好猜了
Dear brother, you're becoming predictable.

1392
01:31:04,450 --> 01:31:06,370
我信任你  你背叛我
I trust you, you betray me.

1393
01:31:06,370 --> 01:31:08,650
一遍又一遍
Round and round in circles we go.

1394
01:31:08,770 --> 01:31:11,130
洛基  人生  是要成长的
See, Loki, life is about... It's about growth.

1395
01:31:11,130 --> 01:31:12,080
是要改变的
It's about change.

1396
01:31:12,080 --> 01:31:15,540
但你好像只想保持原样
But you seem to just wanna stay the same.

1397
01:31:16,150 --> 01:31:17,500
我想说的是
I guess what I'm trying to say

1398
01:31:17,500 --> 01:31:20,600
你永远都只是恶作剧之神
is that you'll always be the God of Mischief,

1399
01:31:21,150 --> 01:31:22,610
但你本可不止如此
but you could be more.

1400
01:31:25,000 --> 01:31:26,820
我就把这个留给你了
I'll just put this over here for you.

1401
01:31:27,150 --> 01:31:30,820
好了  我们都还有地方要去  所以祝你好运了
Anyway, all got places to be, so good luck, I guess.

1402
01:31:36,320 --> 01:31:38,300
好了  你能搞定的
All right, you can figure this out.

1403
01:31:38,350 --> 01:31:39,880
不过是又一艘宇宙飞船罢了
It's just another spaceship.

1404
01:31:53,080 --> 01:31:54,730
忠诚的萨卡人
Loyal Sakaarians,

1405
01:31:54,810 --> 01:31:58,560
雷王偷了我的飞船和我最爱的冠军
Lord of Thunder has stolen my ship and my favorite champion.

1406
01:31:59,730 --> 01:32:03,100
萨卡人  升空  把他打下来
Sakaarians, take to the skies. Bring him down.

1407
01:32:03,100 --> 01:32:04,980
不要让他离开这个星球
Do not let him leave this planet.

1408
01:32:17,820 --> 01:32:19,630
-打得不错  -谢谢
- Good shot! - Thanks.

1409
01:32:22,090 --> 01:32:23,120
开门
Open the doors.

1410
01:32:23,120 --> 01:32:24,060
好
Okay.

1411
01:32:29,530 --> 01:32:31,830
我希望你比看起来要坚强一些
I hope that you're tougher than you look.

1412
01:32:31,830 --> 01:32:32,800
为什么
Why?

1413
01:32:45,120 --> 01:32:47,430
我们不该反击什么的吗
Shouldn't we be shooting back or something?

1414
01:32:47,430 --> 01:32:48,420
是应该
Yes, we should.

1415
01:32:48,970 --> 01:32:50,540
这船上的武器在哪里
Where are the guns on this ship?

1416
01:32:50,590 --> 01:32:52,020
没有武器
There aren't any.

1417
01:32:52,040 --> 01:32:53,890
-这是艘消遣船  -什么
- It's a leisure vessel. - What?

1418
01:32:53,890 --> 01:32:57,170
宗师用它来享乐的  群交派对之类的
Grandmaster uses it for his good times, orgies and stuff.

1419
01:32:57,200 --> 01:32:59,780
她刚刚是说宗师用这船办群交派对吗
Did she just say the Grandmaster uses it for orgies?

1420
01:32:59,780 --> 01:33:00,590
是的
Yeah.

1421
01:33:01,150 --> 01:33:02,240
什么都别碰
Don't touch anything.

1422
01:33:22,670 --> 01:33:23,760
不  不
No! No!

1423
01:33:26,930 --> 01:33:28,530
-不  -不
- No! - No!

1424
01:33:35,420 --> 01:33:36,430
进来
Get inside!

1425
01:33:36,740 --> 01:33:37,880
马上
In a minute.

1426
01:33:49,250 --> 01:33:51,040
我该去帮帮她  你过来开
I should probably go and help. Here, take the wheel.

1427
01:33:51,040 --> 01:33:52,840
不行  我不会开这个
No. I don't know how to fly one of these.

1428
01:33:52,840 --> 01:33:54,660
你是个科学家  用你的博士学位去搞明白
You're a scientist. Use one of your PhDs.

1429
01:33:54,660 --> 01:33:58,490
那些学位都不是外星飞船驾驶啊
None of them are for flying alien spaceships!

1430
