好吧  拜托
Okay, come on.

1431
01:34:33,760 --> 01:34:35,440
这上面肯定有枪的
There's gotta be a gun on this thing.

1432
01:34:35,850 --> 01:34:37,080
那看起来好像是枪
That looks like a gun.

1433
01:34:38,090 --> 01:34:41,480
今天我生日  今天我生日
It's my birthday. It's my birthday.

1434
01:34:41,480 --> 01:34:43,950
今天我生日
It's my birthday.

1435
01:34:50,850 --> 01:34:52,010
好啊
Yeah!

1436
01:35:09,220 --> 01:35:11,770
伙计们  我们马上就要进入恶魔屁眼了
Guys, we're coming up on the Devil's Anus!

1437
01:35:18,410 --> 01:35:19,680
在那儿
There she is.

1438
01:35:19,680 --> 01:35:21,160
我们逃离的途径
Our ticket out of here.

1439
01:35:22,160 --> 01:35:23,420
这是什么
Hey, what's this?

1440
01:35:28,510 --> 01:35:29,230
谢谢
Thank you.

1441
01:35:29,230 --> 01:35:32,230
老兄  我们要跳上那艘超大飞船离开这里
Hey, man. We're about to jump on that ginormous spaceship.

1442
01:35:32,230 --> 01:35:33,050
要一起来吗
You wanna come?

1443
01:35:33,750 --> 01:35:37,930
你们看起来确实急需一位领袖
You do seem like you're in desperate need of leadership.

1444
01:35:37,930 --> 01:35:39,040
谢谢
Why, thank you.

1445
01:35:43,160 --> 01:35:44,500
来了
Here we go.

1446
01:35:51,210 --> 01:35:52,110
该死
Shit.

1447
01:36:09,280 --> 01:36:11,200
阿斯加德人民
Asgardians...

1448
01:36:11,470 --> 01:36:14,020
有不知好歹的人
Some misguided soul

1449
01:36:14,600 --> 01:36:16,780
偷走了彩虹桥之剑
has stolen the Bifrost sword.

1450
01:36:17,020 --> 01:36:18,940
告诉我们它在哪里
Tell us where it is

1451
01:36:19,340 --> 01:36:22,000
否则后果自负
or there will be consequences.

1452
01:36:25,890 --> 01:36:27,460
严重的后果
Bad ones.

1453
01:36:30,230 --> 01:36:31,130
有人说吗
Well?

1454
01:36:38,380 --> 01:36:39,470
你
You.

1455
01:36:42,340 --> 01:36:44,280
不  住手
No! Stop!

1456
01:36:46,850 --> 01:36:47,580
求你们
Please.

1457
01:37:15,740 --> 01:37:19,550
动手啊  处刑人
Well? Executioner?

1458
01:37:24,980 --> 01:37:25,670
等等
Wait!

1459
01:37:26,300 --> 01:37:27,050
等等
Wait!

1460
01:37:29,570 --> 01:37:30,870
我知道剑在哪
I know where the sword is.

1461
01:38:13,560 --> 01:38:15,350
没想到我还能再回来
I never thought I'd be back here.

1462
01:38:19,450 --> 01:38:21,010
我以为会更美一些呢
I thought it'd be a lot nicer.

1463
01:38:21,330 --> 01:38:24,720
倒不是说它不美  只是着火了
I mean, not that it's not nice. It's just, it's on fire.

1464
01:38:24,720 --> 01:38:26,170
看  山上
Here, up here in the mountains.

1465
01:38:26,170 --> 01:38:28,500
有热信号  那里聚集了很多人
Heat signatures. People clustered together.

1466
01:38:28,500 --> 01:38:29,600
她要去找他们了
She's coming for them.

1467
01:38:29,600 --> 01:38:31,950
好  把我丢在王宫  我去引开她
Okay, drop me off at the palace and I'll draw her away.

1468
01:38:31,950 --> 01:38:33,140
你想害死自己吗
And get yourself killed?

1469
01:38:33,140 --> 01:38:34,780
困在那里的人才是最重要的
The people trapped down there are all that matters.

1470
01:38:34,780 --> 01:38:36,010
我去应付海拉时
While I'm dealing with Hela,

1471
01:38:36,010 --> 01:38:37,990
你们得疏散阿斯加德的人民
I need you two to help get everyone off Asgard.

1472
01:38:37,990 --> 01:38:39,740
我们要怎么做啊
How the hell are we supposed to do that?

1473
01:38:40,270 --> 01:38:41,760
我在地面上有人接应
I have a man on the ground.

1474
01:38:47,900 --> 01:38:48,980
阿斯加德人民
Asgard.

1475
01:38:52,150 --> 01:38:53,040
她来了
She's here.

1476
01:39:05,150 --> 01:39:06,740
这下飞船有火力了
Now the ship has a gun.

1477
01:39:06,740 --> 01:39:08,140
交给我吧
I'll take it from here.

1478
01:39:09,020 --> 01:39:11,830
我在武器库发现了这个
I found this in the armory.

1479
01:39:15,400 --> 01:39:16,130
祝你好运
Good luck.

1480
01:39:18,120 --> 01:39:18,970
陛下
Your Majesty...

1481
01:39:21,510 --> 01:39:22,250
别死了
Don't die.

1482
01:39:25,300 --> 01:39:26,290
你懂我意思的
You know what I mean.

1483
01:40:26,040 --> 01:40:27,330
别停步
We must keep moving!

1484
01:40:28,600 --> 01:40:30,030
去彩虹桥
Go to the Bifrost!

1485
01:41:12,870 --> 01:41:13,750
姐姐
Sister.

1486
01:41:16,370 --> 01:41:17,830
你还活着
You're still alive.

1487
01:41:18,230 --> 01:41:21,720
我喜欢你对这里的改造  重装修了啊
I love what you've done with the place. Redecorating, I see.

1488
01:41:21,720 --> 01:41:24,000
看来我们父亲解决
It seems our father's solution

1489
01:41:24,000 --> 01:41:27,120
所有问题的思路都是掩盖
to every problem was to cover it up.

1490
01:41:28,150 --> 01:41:29,550
